    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚和中国：澳大利亚作家死刑威胁，两国关系回升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-rebound-ties-threatened-by-death-sentence-australian-writer-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京一家法院周一判处澳大利亚作家杨恒均死刑缓期执行，并威胁在北京与堪培拉之间多年紧张关系之后，双边关系近期将出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-rebound-ties-threatened-by-death-sentence-australian-writer-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 05:34:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴布亚绑架一年后新西兰呼吁释放新西兰飞行员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-calls-kiwi-pilot-be-freed-year-after-papua-kidnapping-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰外交部长周一表示，新西兰呼吁立即释放新西兰飞行员菲利普·梅尔滕斯，一年前他在印度尼西亚巴布亚地区被叛军劫持为人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-calls-kiwi-pilot-be-freed-year-after-papua-kidnapping-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 05:31:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰预计六月发布国防能力报告</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-expects-defence-capability-report-june-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰国防部长朱迪思·柯林斯周一表示，她预计将在六月收到对该国国防能力的审查，这是该国军队现代化的最新一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-expects-defence-capability-report-june-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于大宗商品价格下跌，印度尼西亚 2023 年 GDP 增速放缓至 5.1%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-2023-gdp-growth-slows-51-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大宗商品价格下跌打击了出口以及紧缩的货币政策抑制了需求，印度尼西亚去年的年度经济增长率略有下降，但仍保持在 5.05% 的稳定水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-2023-gdp-growth-slows-51-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:20:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳洲航空前往公平工作委员会解决与飞行员的薪酬纠纷</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/qantas-heads-fair-work-commission-sort-pay-dispute-with-pilots-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚航空公司周一将前往该国公平工作委员会，就其与西澳大利亚一家子公司的飞行员之间的薪酬相关纠纷寻求仲裁，这些飞行员​​已三度否决了一项新的企业交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/qantas-heads-fair-work-commission-sort-pay-dispute-with-pilots-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:11:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚总统候选人在选举前发表和解言论</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-hopefuls-strike-conciliatory-note-ahead-election-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着争夺世界第三大民主国家的激烈竞争进入最后阶段，印度尼西亚总统候选人在最新的电视辩论中发表了和解言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-presidential-hopefuls-strike-conciliatory-note-ahead-election-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 03:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国通胀近三年来最低，但央行可能维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-inflation-lowest-nearly-three-years-commerce-ministry-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一数据显示，泰国1月份年度总体消费者通胀率降至35个月以来的最低水平，商务部表示，预计第一季度物价压力将进一步缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/thai-inflation-lowest-nearly-three-years-commerce-ministry-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 03:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚战争英雄对有关他参与阿富汗非法杀戮的报道的诽谤裁决提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-war-hero-appeals-defamation-ruling-reports-he-was-complicit-afghan-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚一家法院周一开始审理一名功勋战争英雄的上诉，他正在对法院的一项诽谤裁决进行抗争，该裁决发现媒体团体已经证明了他们的报道，他参与了阿富汗境内四名阿富汗人的非法杀害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-war-hero-appeals-defamation-ruling-reports-he-was-complicit-afghan-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 03:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰政府部长在国庆庆祝活动前遭到抗议者质问</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-govt-ministers-heckled-by-protesters-ahead-national-day-celebrations-2024-02-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，新西兰政府部长们抵达怀唐伊镇参加新西兰建国文件《怀唐伊条约》签署周年纪念活动时，遭到了抗议者的质问，他们的讲话被歌曲淹没了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-govt-ministers-heckled-by-protesters-ahead-national-day-celebrations-2024-02-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 03:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
